Package backend

Class SampleAverage

java.lang.Object
backend.Sample
backend.SampleAverage
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SampleAverage
extends Sample
SampleAverage extends Sample, refers to several Samples grouped as one. Usually SampleAverage is used to represent several Samples of one region or ethnicity.
